title: Mr Falafel
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Palestinian
description: Market food stall turned little shop near where the stall was. Food is mostly vegan except for halloumi and feta cheese. Falafel in wraps with sauces and pickles in addition to other Arabic food such as batata harra, hummus, fries, fatoosh, ful medames.
